      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARA'S LOKI (1) could manage only fourth over 520m at this track last time when gave a start and was beaten 10 lengths in a Grade 5 (30.83). Expected to enjoy the longer journey for the first time here. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from seven starts. Has ability and looks hard to stop. SMOKIN' JILL (2) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (35.42) at this track. Cannot be left out. MAGGIE'S SONG (3) has missed the placings at her last couple but was in the money three back when third (25.62) at Q Lakeside in a Grade 5. Can improve sharply here. FLAMING VALORA (7) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
